03_Hiding_Text_in_Audio
Aim: Hide and extract a text file inside an audio file.
Procedure (Hiding):

Place "A.txt" (text) and "sound.mp3" (audio) on the desktop.

Open Command Prompt and navigate to the desktop.

Run: copy /b A.txt + sound.mp3 newfile.mp3 to create "newfile.mp3".
Retrieval:

Open "newfile.mp3" with Notepad; the hidden text appears at the end.
Result: Successfully hid and extracted text within an audio file.
