________________________________________________________________________________________

13_Hiding_ZIP_in_Image
Aim: Hide a ZIP file within an image.
Procedure:

Place "cover.jpg" (image) and "secret.zip" (ZIP file) in the same folder.

Merge them using:

Copy
copy /b cover.jpg + secret.zip hidden.jpg  
Retrieval:

Rename the output file to extract the ZIP:

Copy
ren hidden.jpg secret.zip  
Result: Successfully hid and retrieved the ZIP file within an image.
